name: RYN_WHT_GENO_PHENO_SCREEN
description: Stores data for Ryan White CAREWare Geno/Pheno Screenings.

columns.name: REGISTRY_DATA_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier (.1 item) for the registry data record.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: RW_GENO_PHENO_DATE
columns.description: The date on which the Geno/Pheno screening took place.

columns.name: RW_GENOPHENO_RSLT_C_NAME
columns.description: The result of the Geno/Pheno screening.

columns.name: RW_GENO_PHENO_SCORE
columns.description: The numerical score of the Geno/Pheno screening.

columns.name: RW_GENO_PHENO_CMTS
columns.description: The comments for the Geno/Pheno screening.
